---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Releases — GinkgoQ" description="See the public changelog and release notes for GinkgoQ updates.">
  <section class="releases-hero container" aria-labelledby="releases-heading">
    <span class="eyebrow">Changelog</span>
    <h1 id="releases-heading">Release notes and updates</h1>
    <p class="lead">Track what’s new at GinkgoQ: article releases, site updates, and public improvements to our AI writing and product thinking.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="releases-body container">
    <article class="release-card">
      <p class="release-meta">2026-05-22 · Release</p>
      <h2>Public site and metadata updates</h2>
      <p>Added RSS sidebar links, Start here guidance, public roadmap, and review page structure for citations and copy-link headings.</p>
    </article>

    <article class="release-card">
      <p class="release-meta">2026-04-15 · Update</p>
      <h2>New research notes and blog content</h2>
      <p>Published new Research Notes items, refreshed the blog sidebar, and improved metadata for per-post SEO.</p>
    </article>

    <p class="release-summary">This page will continue to document major site changes and content milestones. Check back for future updates.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .releases-hero {
    padding: 90px 0 50px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }

  .releases-hero h1 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 1.1rem 0 1.4rem;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .releases-body {
    padding: 64px 0 96px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .release-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
  }

  .release-meta {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  .release-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.85rem;
  }

  .release-summary {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }
</style>
